headline: 3 Consumer Stocks We Keep Off Our Radar
summary: The performance of consumer discretionary businesses is closely linked to economic cycles. Thankfully for the industry, all signs are pointing up as discretionary stocks have gained 19.9% over the past six months, beating the S&P 500’s 15.6% return.
